<h1>Terms of Use</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: February 7, 2026</p>

<p>These Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your use of the "sugosu" application ("the App") provided by mamonis.studio ("we"). By using the App, you agree to these Terms.</p>

<h2>1. Service Description</h2>
<p>The App integrates environmental data (temperature, humidity, barometric pressure, PM2.5, UV, pollen, precipitation) with health records to provide a comfort score.</p>

<h2>2. Medical Disclaimer</h2>
<p>This App is not a medical application. All information displayed (scores, AI analysis, health predictions, etc.) is for reference only and is not intended for medical diagnosis, treatment, or prevention. If you have health concerns, please consult a healthcare professional. We are not liable for any damages resulting from decisions based on this App's information.</p>

<h2>3. Data</h2>
<p>All App data is stored on your device. We are not responsible for data loss due to device failure, loss, or app deletion. We recommend using the export feature to back up important data.</p>

<h2>4. Environmental Data Accuracy</h2>
<p>Environmental data is retrieved from the Open-Meteo API. We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of this data. Data may be unavailable due to network or API outages.</p>

<h2>5. Purchases</h2>
<p>Premium features are available via in-app purchases through the App Store / Google Play.</p>
<ul>
